---
title: Striploin Steak and Tarragon Cream Sauce with Sweet Potato Mash and Roasted Veggie Duo
description: Steak and mushrooms are a match made in heaven. For this dish, tender striploin steak is topped with a savoury mushroom and tarragon cream sauce that will make any day feel like a special occasion.
